Moses foldable shopping bag

Super cute shopping bag with images of little owls on it. The bag is extra sturdy and offers enough space for all your groceries and other stuff. It can be folded up to a small size, so that you can always take it with you easily.

Specifications:

Age: 3+ years
Material: polyester
Dimensions: 50 x 70 cm (L x H)
Dimensions (folded): 13 x 13 cm
Content: 10 liters
